ADDITIONAL INFORMATION:

Girls Of Grace is a thematic collection of 10 worship songs from Point Of Grace featuring some of today's top female Christian artists. Building on the precedence of their previous projects and aimed at providing direction into the lives of teenage girls world-wise, this new praise and worship album from Point Of Grace will provide listeners with refreshed hearts, renewed self-confidence and a better understanding of their daily walk with God.
